name: Base58

values.name: decode
values.comment:
Decodes turns a string into its original BigInt
        "ANYBx47k26vP81XFbQXh6XKUj7ptQRJMLt"
            |> Base58.decode
        == BigInt.fromString "146192635802076751054841979942155177482410195601230638449945"

values.name: encode
values.comment:
Encode turns a big int into a string
        BigInt.fromString "146192635802076751054841979942155177482410195601230638449945"
            |> Base58.encode
        == "ANYBx47k26vP81XFbQXh6XKUj7ptQRJMLt"
